3.Fol. 6. That 1 Cor. 5. 5. to deliver ſuch a one to Satan, is not
meant of ſuſpenſion or excommunication from the Sacrament;
which the other hold.

div.p:
And for that ten to one, being converted ſo as he ſayes;
Quere, Whether it is not ten to one any will be a converted,
but rather hardned?
